  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Combine almond flour and melted butter in a bowl until well mixed. If using jelly, stir it into the mixture.",
    "Press the crumble base evenly onto a lined baking sheet or pie dish.",
    "Top with chopped almonds on top of the crumble base.",
    "Bake for 20-25 minutes or until golden brown and bubbly at the edges.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool before serving."
